    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/pansidong/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">竹簡</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar30 main-title-rating" title="还行"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2011-01-04"
      class="main-meta">2011-01-04 09:30:18</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_4562968_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  史景迁的这本《前朝梦忆——张岱的浮华与苍凉》，由广西师大出版，素净的暗草绿色，低调的烫金英文小字，捧在手里，能感觉到布面一般的纹理与质感，于是，我便上当了。  豆瓣上的书评，竟然多是四星至五星。更有几个似乎已经在报刊上发表了书评的读者，满篇都是溢美之辞——莫...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/4562968/#comments">(10回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">19有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_4562968_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_4562968_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










